      "message": "In cases where we mix revisioned and revision-less sources, the order is reversed here. Previously the revision-less source would be first. Now it will be the last, if any revisioned sources are present. This is alright, but it should be described somewhere and ideally covered with a test - having both revision-less and a revisioned sources and assert which one a wildcard import resolves to.",
